                  <p>Twin brother and sister <persName ref="#dipper">Dipper</persName> and <persName
                        ref="#mabel">Mabel</persName> are in for an unexpected adventure when <rs
                        ref="#mabel #dipper">they</rs> spend the summer with <rs
                        ref="#mabel #dipper">their</rs>
                     <rs ref="#stan">great uncle</rs> in the mysterious town of <placeName
                        ref="#gravityFalls">Gravity Falls</placeName>. Upon <rs ref="#mabel #dipper"
                        >their</rs> arrival, <persName ref="#dipper">Dipper</persName> and <persName
                        ref="#mabel">Mabel</persName>'s <rs ref="#stan">great uncle</rs> enlists <rs
                        ref="#mabel #dipper">them</rs> to run the <placeName ref="#mysteryShack"
                        >Mystery Shack</placeName>, a fun tourist trap <rs ref="#stan">he</rs> owns
                     that overcharges unsuspecting customers. Although <persName ref="#dipper"
                        >Dipper</persName> and <persName ref="#mabel">Mabel</persName> quickly
                     discover the <placeName ref="#mysteryShack">Mystery Shack</placeName> itself is
                     a hoax, <rs ref="#mabel #dipper">they</rs> sense there is something strange
                     about <rs ref="#mabel #dipper">their</rs> new <rs ref="#gravityFalls">town</rs>
                     and together <rs ref="#mabel #dipper">they</rs> begin to unlock the secrets of
                        <placeName ref="#gravityFalls">Gravity Falls</placeName>.</p>
